          },
          "reviewBody": "Pirates of Balewadi!!!\nSome of teachers knowledge is ridiculous, a teacher mentioned in PTM that grammar concept changes based on grade of student, absurd and laughable.\nYou name any junk food, be it pizza, burger, ice-cream. The school has a outlet for it. They don't mind to make money at the expense of your kids health and habit.\nFirst of all fee is sky rocketing and in case you miss paying the fee then instead of reminding for payment, school charge 3% per month (Yes, 36% per annum) as the late fee.\nIf you find any other school, please save yourselves.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
