            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This school is problem for nearby residents in various societies. The main problem is mismanagement of traffic on adjecent road. The school guards are incapable to handle the road traffic due to parking of cars on road by  parents of students. The management of school should take serious note of this problem. Only taking the huge fees and doing this school business is not good.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
