            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is not a school, but a business . They are interested in only money to open new branches elsewhere. Every year the fees is hiked to provide even worse teaching/services/facilities.\n\nIf the offline teaching was bad, the online is worse. My 9 year old seems to have better knowledge and better grasp of English compared to the teachers.  The support staff at the school don't respond to queries properly.\n\nThe premises is not great. Children need to use a lift to reach the classroom!!! Management is also terrible. Please avoid this school.",
          "publisher": {
